or white stands for Theravada Buddhism.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/flags/flagtemplate_th.html |title=Flag Description: Thailand |work=World Factbook |publisher=[[Central Intelligence Agency|CIA]] |accessdate=June 21, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615131500/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/flags/flagtemplate_th.html |archivedate=June 15, 2013 |df= }}</ref> |}
